    dc:description "FIGURES 7–9. Male habitus of Anoplophora spp. 7, Anoplophora cheni Bi & N. Ohbayashi, 2015; 8, A. multimaculata (Xie & Wang, 2015); 9, A. flavomaculata (Gressitt, 1935)." ;
